						               													<description>Though the massively mutated Dark Stone Scorpions are renowned for their thick shells, potent poison, and razor-edged claws that can snap a man in two with a single powerful pinch, the nightmarish Bone Scorpions that roam the alien desert dunes of the Blasted Wastes and the shadowy groves within the Forest of the Dead are perhaps more terrifying. Equal in size and ferocity with their earthly counterparts, the Bone Scorpions are more agile and quick to enrage, lashing out with the lightning-fast retaliatory strikes of their stinging tails at any that draw too near.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This Alternate Enemy Pack converts the terrifying and poisonous Dark Stone Scorpions into the nightmarish Bone Scorpions for use in the Blasted Wastes and Forest of the Dead OtherWorlds! There are 2 XL Dark Stone Scorpion models included to paint in this alternate color scheme, 1 Blasted Wastes Artifact card, and all of the Threat Cards needed to add them to your games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
